            <scopecontent id="aspace_14f20f60909efa7dfd6c5633af8be7cc">
               <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
               <p>This series consists chiefly of drafts of writings by E. F. Benson, including 41 short stories, the novel <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Paul</part>
                  </title>, one untitled and evidently unpublished novel, and a review of "Jérusalem" by Pierre Loti. A large portion of the drafts are corrected in the hand of the author or others. Unless otherwise indicated, all materials are holograph or typescript drafts (original or carbon).</p>
            </scopecontent>
