               <p>This series consists of incoming and outgoing correspondence of the literary agency, The Authors' Syndicate, Ltd., relating to the writings of E. F. Benson. Correspondents include E. F. Benson, William M. Colles, William Heinemann, and other agents, editors, and publishers. Correspondence consists of holograph and typescript letters (most signed), retained copies of letters in secretarial hands, carbon copies of letters, secretarial notes, and telegrams.</p>
